Mustafā ibn Ibrāhīm [al-Maddāh al-Qinalī] (d. after 1151 H [1738 CE]

md:note.div:
Teksten er en historien om Egypten under det Osmaniske rige 1688 til 1737.
Købt i Kairo i 1763 af Frederik Christian von Haven (d. 1763), der var deltager i Carsten Niebuhr ekspeditionen til mellemøsten i 1761-1763.
Cod. Arab 159.

The text delas with the history of Ottoman Egypt from 1688 to 1737.
Bought in Cairo 1763 by Frederik Christian von Haven (d. 1763), a member of the Carsten Niebuhr expedition in 1761-1763.
